{
  "text": "Kutchinsky's 26-year-old claim-that an increase in pornography (in far-away Denmark, over 20 years) had been inversely correlated with rape levels [CITATION_1] -was a maze of obvious measurement errors, and was discredited decades ago. Marche naively reports it at length here, as if exciting, newsworthy and valid (p.122).",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "29985592"
